column1:
At 6:00 in native Telugu, in the order of popularity and familiarity from highest to least, 
sky is ningi(నింగి), minnu(మిన్ను), vinnu(విన్ను), chadhalu(చదలు), upparam(ఉప్పరం);
moon is nela(నెల), dzaabili(జాబిలి), rEvelugu(రేవెలుగు), togamailu(తొగమైలు), manduraa(మందురా);
country is seema(సీమ), aaNem(ఆణెం), naaDu(నాడు). aaNem has variations like aaNiyam(ఆణియం) and aaNyam(ఆణ్యం) also.
